<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_305_r1l9">Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Frıcʒen <expan>Mayental<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r1l10">als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> den German <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_305_r1l11"><expan>ew<ex>e</ex>rn</expan> brief wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd iſt vns das von des <expan>ew<ex>e</ex>rn</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
