</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_305" id="152r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hadmar von Laber dem
                            <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Friczen
                            <expan>Mayental<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, den German <expan>Rewt<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>e</ex>rn</expan> brief wol
                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>, und ist uns das von des
                                <expan>ew<ex>e</ex>rn</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>getrewlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> leide. Auch hat uns
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> erwirdig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> abbt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Regensp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vormals darumb
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und also
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>burgg<ex>ra</ex>fen</expan> Johansen darumb
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und auch mit
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Mayentaler <expan>selb<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        davon reden lassen. Und <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir auch fürbas
                            <add>noch</add> iht gütes darczu getün, das
                            <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. Wan wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lieb und dinste etc.</ab>
</div>
